=Calligraphy 書法=
==Literature==
===PhD Dissertations===
* [[Amy McNair]]: The politics of calligraphic style in China: Yan Zhenqing (709-785) and the Song literati, The University of Chicago, 1989
* Qianshen Bai: Fu Shan (1607-1684/85) and the transformation of Chinese calligraphy in the seventeenth century, Yale University, 1996
* Bor-hua Wang: Su Shih's art of writing and his Han-shih t'ieh, Columbia University, 1997
* Huiwen Lu: A new imperial style of calligraphy: Stone engravings in Northern Wei Luoyang, 494--534, Princeton University, 2003